      "title": "the environment ; How the day of 'Vyaghara Babala' in Dehiwala is spent",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "Veterinarians say that the three Bengal tiger cubs born at the Dehiwala Zoo are in good health.",
        "These animals have been brought together for public display and local school children have been given the opportunity to name them among the branches."
